Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.36,1:45:01.67,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\q2}沾湿了你的脸颊
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.87,1:45:07.38,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\q2}柔和的天空
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.04,1:45:13.58,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\q2}向远处进发
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.06,1:45:22.17,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\q2}即便只是小小的心灵
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.80,1:45:34.24,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\q2}只是还未丰满的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.70,1:45:38.82,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\q2}向着明天
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.16,1:45:44.99,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\q2}向着怀念的昨天
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.22,1:45:56.51,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\q2}在指间所订下的小小的约定
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.85,1:45:59.96,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\q2}试着去完成吧
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.96,1:46:03.07,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\q2}在时间的尽头
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.07,1:46:11.50,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\q2}将能和你相见的那天藏在胸中
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.56,1:46:17.89,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\q2}只有愿望
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.18,1:46:30.69,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,1000)\q2}直到渐行渐远的未来
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.52,1:46:46.60,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\q2}即便我已无处可寻
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.70,1:46:54.83,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\q2}普照大地的光芒中
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.89,1:47:13.51,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\q2}我会一直在你身边
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.76,1:47:21.95,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\q2}即使是虚无缥缈
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.29,1:47:26.35,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\q2}行将破碎的世界里
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.35,1:47:30.84,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\q2}只要你还在
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.91,1:47:40.37,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\q2}就值得守护
